      "employmentOutlook": "<p>Skilled bakers and pastry professionals are sought by restaurants, hotels, retail bakeries, and specialty markets. Graduates qualify for entry-level roles such as baker, pastry cook, cake decorator, and pastry assistant, with room to grow into lead and production positions.</p><p>(Please note: CPCC does not guarantee employment)</p>",
