      "overview": "<p>Learn the art and science of cosmetology in a simulated salon where you build real client-ready skills.</p><p>You&rsquo;ll develop hands-on fundamentals in hair design, cutting and chemical services, color, skin and nail care, and multicultural techniques&mdash;plus the product knowledge, professionalism, and business basics that prepare you for the State Board of Cosmetic Arts exam and a career behind the chair.</p>",
